headline: AbbVie (ABBV) Updates 2025 EPS Guidance with $823M IPR&D Expense
summary: AbbVie Inc. (NYSE:ABBV) is one of the 7 most undervalued pot stocks to buy according to analysts. On July 3, the company provided an update to its 2025 earnings guidance to account for a pre-tax acquired in-process research and development (IPR&D) and milestones expense of $823 million in the second quarter of 2025.
